#Создание операции:

POST http://localhost:8080/api/operations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dateTime": "2024-01-15T12:30:00",
  "totalAmount": 1500.50,
  "comment": "Покупка продуктов",
  "accountId": 1,
  "marketplaceId": 1,
  "operationTypeId": 2
}


